author: @AlchemyMortgages
text: Literally just spent all morning trying to figure out what was wrong with my settings then saw this video after finding a cross-share manual method LOL.  If you're like me and have an Insta Business Account + the mandatory Facebook Business Page + Personal Facebook Profile, all of my Insta content (whether directly shared via the Insta app or from Canva) is now auto-sharing to my Facebook Business Page when it used to go to my Personal one.  Manual Workaround to get the content onto my personal Fbk profile is: While on my personal fbk page I search for my business page, go into it and click the content I want then to share to my personal feed or story with the option to add notes.  I hope that makes sense and is helpful to people!
